 <body>
  <h1>
   audio_stop_all
  </h1>
  This function will stop
  <i>
   all
  </i>
  sounds that are currently playing.
  <h4>
   Syntax:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">audio_stop_all();
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">N/A
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">if !global.SFX
{
    audio_stop_all();
}
</code></pre>
  The above code checks the global variable "SFX" and if it returns
  <span>
   false
  </span>
  , it will stop all sounds that are currently playing.
 </body>
